summary: If you like horror movies, and haven't heard/seen Dead Meat, you should check him out. He does kill counts as well as podcasts...
body:
If you like horror movies, and haven’t heard/seen Dead Meat, you should check him out. He does kill counts as well as podcasts with his girlfriend (they’re really cute together, and deserves the world). He’s also an lgbt supporter. The podcast video I’m about to talk about, is about a movie I can’t stand (its gross/disturbing) however, Chelsea really likes the movie, and gives actually good points on why she likes it (ie: the nudity wasn’t really actual nudity, the actresses were treated good, etc.) I’d give it a listen, and I don’t even like this movie (I get queasy very easily).

I’m taking about Human Centipede

summary: Breathless.
title: Breathless.
body:
This is just a lil something something because I’m feeling inspired. 

I FINALLY got a request in my messages to do a little blurb about breathless kisses with Colby… Here we goooo!




Breathless kisses with Colby

You would wake up to him rubbing your back and watching you sleep
“Good morning babe” he’d say as he would give you a warm smile. At this moment all you can do is say good morning back and lean in to give him a kiss. This kiss wasn’t just any kiss though, this kiss happened the morning after the two of you made love for the first time, this kiss wasn’t only needed but it was wanted. The moment you looked into Colby’s ocean blue eyes you fell for him all over again. You leaned in slowly and touched noses. You closed your eyes just feeling how close he was at this moment. You felt his breath intermingle with yours in between your lips. Colby reached up to finger comb the back of your hair and you could hear him chuckle. “You are so beautiful y/n” he says before closing his eyes too. At this moment, it wasn’t about the anticipation of the kiss, it was about the moment before the kiss. That moment that leaves you breathless.
